<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Balthasar von Maßbach, Domherr von Würzburg und Propst von Ansbach</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache bei dem Streit der Klara Tetzel, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, wegen beschlagnahmten Weins und teilt mit, dass sie wegen Krankheit von ihrem Diener Johann Amman vertreten wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_51" id="25r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_51_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Balthaſar von Maſpach <expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l2">cʒu <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd Probſt cʒu Onlſpach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_51_r1l4">Erſamer vnd lıeber 
<add><ab facs="#facs_51_r1l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> </ab></add> Als vvir nehſt <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gebeten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von frawn Claren der Jobs Tecʒlin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin wegen / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l6">hat vns dıeſelbe vnſer burgerin cʒu vviſſen getan / vvie daʒ ſie von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l8">krankheit irs leibs 
<add><ab facs="#facs_51_line_1576492520756_8771"><expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> ye ſelber nıht hinab <expan>gecʒieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ir </del> Jr vveine </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l9"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> müg / vnd darümb ſo hab ſıe dem <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Amman Jrem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l10">diener 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan></del> gewalt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jren vvein von <expan>Jre<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l11">wegen vnd an <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtat cʒu vertreten / Als ew das derſelb <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Amman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l12">ſelber auch wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werde <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / daʒ Jr ew <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l13">burgerin diener darẏnne durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>günſtiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l14">laſſen wöllet Als etc das wollen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Martıni </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_51" id="25r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Balthasar von Maspach,
                            <expan>tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        und probst czu Onlspach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan></add>, als wir nehst
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gebeten
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von frawn Claren, der Jobs Teczlin,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin, wegen. Also hat uns
                        dieselbe unser burgerin czu wissen getan, wie daz sie von krankheit irs
                        leibs <add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> ye selber niht hinab
                                <expan>geczieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ir weine
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> müg; und darümb so hab sie dem
                                <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Amman, irem diener, gewalt
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        iren wein von <expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen und an
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu vertreten, als ew das derselb
                                <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Amman selber auch wol
                                <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werde.
                            <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., daz ir ew
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin diener darynne durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllet, als etc. Das wollen
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
                        Martini.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
